{"tid":2446354,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)顫慄異次元 撕裂地平線 曬撚氣1-2","createTime":"2021-03-14T11:30:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T19:57:55.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"869f3017fc6b114c877fe1231d3d87b2bd4cfae7","tid":2446354,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T11:30:29.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">支肺已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=wSR7%2FpLLUFbraZn9MQiPfN6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=94762e5d\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=wSR7%2FpLLUFbraZn9MQiPfN6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=024963c4\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=wSR7%2FpLLUFbraZn9MQiPfN6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=6f727859\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/3/3d/Pandorum-Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F3%2F3d%2FPandorum-Poster.jpg&h=a3bcdf0b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/8c/Event_horizon_ver1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F8%2F8c%2FEvent_horizon_ver1.jpg&h=368d580f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/5/57/Silent_hill.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F5%2F57%2FSilent_hill.jpg&h=082b8fbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.經過數百年的發展，人類文明高度進化，他們逐漸將觸角伸向宇宙深處。然而，隨著人口激增，有限的資源消耗殆盡。到2174年，地球資源嚴重匱乏，資源爭奪戰達到頂峰。為了尋求新的生存樂土，人類向宇宙發射了名為&ldquo;極樂世界&rdquo;的宇宙飛船，開始漫長、未知的宇宙探索。經過長時間的深度睡眠，船員鮑爾（本&middot;福斯特Ben Foster 飾）和佩頓上尉（丹尼斯&middot;奎德Dennis Quaid 飾）相繼醒來。不知出於何種原因，他們完全忘記了航行的目的和任務。鮑爾與佩頓合作檢查飛船，很快便發現其他同伴的屍體，這些昔日的伙伴死狀恐怖。而且他們似乎不是僅存的生命體，一種神秘的生物仍在威脅著他們的生命......<br />\n<br />\n2.西元2040年，政府秘密製造的「Event Horizon號」太空船，要以新研發的重力驅動系統，製造出人造黑洞以進行時空重疊，可瞬間跳躍至數光年甚至數千光年以外之地，用來縮短太空探索時間的新科技。但該船在啟動首次的重力跳躍後，便一去不回，直到2047年才重新現身於海王星附近..<br />\n<br />\n3.蘿絲（Rose Da Silva）自小收養的女兒雪倫（Sharon Da Silva）患有夢遊症且多次提及小鎮『沉默之丘』。為尋求答案，蘿絲不顧丈夫克里斯席瓦（Christopher Da Silva）的反對於一天晚上帶著雪倫前往沉默之丘。在接近小鎮時二人被女警西碧兒（Cybil Bennett）追捕（因懷疑蘿絲企圖遺棄雪倫），蘿絲於驅車擺脫追捕時突然看見一女孩在路上出現，為閃避而撞上路邊失去知覺。蘿絲於醒來時發現雪倫竟已失蹤，白霧籠罩著一切，無數灰燼從天上持續地飄落。<br />\n<br />\n4.海瑟梅森和父親哈利梅森一直以來都在躲避不明力量的恐怖追殺。她18歲生日當晚，在夢魘纏身和父親神秘失蹤的詭譎情況下，海瑟發現自己原來從未瞭解「真正的自己」。隨著啟示錄的指引，她踏入了一個危機四伏、狂暴絕倫，可能令她永世不得脫身的邪惡世界&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n8 40PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=wSR7%2FpLLUFbraZn9MQiPfN6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=71a76351\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=wSR7%2FpLLUFbraZn9MQiPfN6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=c79e19ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"099ed3177957c2cc6842729e27b0efa0a2af565a","tid":2446354,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T11:33:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cbbbd84e241547804d5dc48746610c2b8fa6b8e","tid":2446354,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T12:23:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b28335d5121ef7f3e181d72ebf7884d1d52f51ac","tid":2446354,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T15:25:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82ed2af775b66e23b1656f72e543b722f7c38988","tid":2446354,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:50:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81d373b28d746a57b49e3897ab4b3a328e22aaab","tid":2446354,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T19:57:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}